	format ("SPENCER: Great…\n"
		"Now there are two weird TEAMS up to no good.\p"
		"They all seem to be headed to MT. CHIMNEY.\N"
		"I've got a bad feeling about this.\p"
		"I'm going to go to MT. CHIMNEY and make sure nothing bad happens.\p"
		"You should come join me whenever you can!")
}

